# {{ name }} API

## Architecture
- ASP.NET Core + FastEndpoints (not controllers)
- PostgreSQL + EF Core
- ErrorOr for error handling
- IScopedService auto-registration

## Project Structure
- `{{ name }}.Host/` — API host
- `Core/` — business logic, auth, persistence
- `Shared/` — DTOs, contracts, enums
- `{{ name }}.SourceGenerator/` — permissions generator
- `Tests/` — unit + integration tests

## Patterns
- Endpoints in `{{ name }}.Host/Features/{Feature}/`
- Services implement `IScopedService` for auto-DI
- Methods return `ErrorOr<T>`
- Use `IApplicationRepository<T>` for data access
- Validators use `FluentValidation` in `Core/Common/Requests/`

## Build & Test
```bash
dotnet build
dotnet test
dotnet run --project {{ name }}.Host
```

## Migrations
```bash
dotnet ef migrations add {Name} --project {{ name }}.Host --context ApplicationDbContext
```
